<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٤ - <span class="c2">(٧٢٩)</span> وَحَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2102">زُهَيْرُ بْنُ حَرْبٍ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4168">وَعُبَيْدُ اللهِ بْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى - وَهُوَ ابْنُ سَعِيدٍ </a>-، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ</a> <span class="c2">(ح)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>